cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV

This paper is about locomotion control for legged robots, which falls under the field of robotics (cs.RO). The paper proposes a novel algorithm for adapting to soft terrain, which involves estimating terrain compliance in real-time, which falls under the field of control systems (cs.SY). The algorithm also uses knowledge of the terrain to generate an optimal solution, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.AI). The paper also includes simulation and experimental results, which involve data analysis and visualization (cs.LG) and computer vision techniques for terrain detection (cs.CV).
